message.body: How excited are you for college next year?!
ahh will!!! its been too long since we've hung out! Eeeep im so so excited!! I cant wait to meet all the new people and take great classes. Are you excited for emory? Kelly's going there.
Kelly who? Also you're going to school with lily!! Yayayayay. Wesleyan is supah koool. Yeah we needa hang out like during regents week or something.

Ohhh alright, I don't know her that well but I'll see her there! Also Megan rosa from delta is going to Emory. Fun. Move in day is August 25!! Yeah I have a lot of stuff to do, even though there are only 10 days of school left, but we will def see each other this summer before college!
Lmao delta party at Wesleyan! That will be fun. Yeah in a week or so when I have less work we will plan something forreals
